---
// src/components/home/HeroModern.astro
---
<section class="relative z-20 -mt-20 md:-mt-32 py-16 md:py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  
  <div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden bg-gray-900 p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(255,255,255,0.15)] border border-white/50">
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900/95 via-gray-900/80 to-gray-800/40 pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      
      <div class="text-white space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight">
          Seguridad <br/>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-omerhsa-primary to-blue-300">Inteligente</span> <br/>
          para tu vida.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 max-w-lg leading-relaxed shadow-sm">
          Gestiona riesgos y protege tu patrimonio con la solidez de OMERHSA. Más de 20 años blindando el futuro de las familias y empresas en Honduras.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-2xl lg:ml-auto max-w-md w-full border border-gray-100/20 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Cotiza tu Seguro</h3>
          <span class="bg-omerhsa-light text-omerhsa-primary text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Cotización Rápida</span>
        </div>

        <form action="/cotizar" class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 mb-1 pb-4">Tipo de Protección</label>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
              <button type="button" class="px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-omerhsa-primary text-white text-sm font-medium shadow-md transition hover:scale-105 uppercase">Vehículos</button>
              <button type="button" class="px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition uppercase">Incendio</button>
              <button type="button" class="px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition uppercase">Vida</button>
              <button type="button" class="px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition uppercase">Gastos médicos</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="w-full py-4 bg-gray-900 hover:bg-omerhsa-dark text-white rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2 group">
            Iniciar Cotización
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>